description.@value: 本文篇の第3巻：本書には、調査範囲の地名索引のほかに、踏査範囲の地理、調査経路の自然環境や中央アジアからロシアに至るルート情報、さらに当該地域への旅行の際の携行品や荷物搬送方法、旅行の際の注意書きなども含む。

Volume 3: In addition to the index of expedition place names, the volume includes the geography of the expedition places, environmental and route information from Central Asia to Russia; as well as regional travel information, including advice on things to bring on a trip to the region and international parcel information.
